        'jsonld_faq_1_answer' => 'Start your path with only ₱10,000, gaining complete access to our crypto investment tools and assistance.',
        'jsonld_faq_2_question' => 'Is previous investment knowledge required?',
        'jsonld_faq_2_answer' => 'No. Our platform suits newcomers and seasoned investors alike, offering support throughout the process.',
        'jsonld_faq_3_question' => 'When can returns be expected?',
        'jsonld_faq_3_answer' => 'Results vary based on selected approach and market dynamics. Our tools support informed decisions with clear risk visibility.',
